features: 【Increase Safety】: The deer warning device serves as an essential automotive accessory, particularly invaluable for those residing in rural or wild areas. The perforated whistle will emit a loud whistle by the wind, which can alert deer, elk, moose, antelope, and kangaroo approaching vehicles, effectively avoiding collisions between animals and vehicles.

【Quality Material】: The dual structure deer warning whistle is made of ABS plastic material, waterproof, safe, robust, reliable and durable. The appearance of atmosphere, feel delicate, tasteless, can withstand outdoor extreme temperature. It works even in very hot and cold weather conditions. The whistle is self-adhesive, which makes it more stable and won't damage your car paint.

【Dual Construction】: These vehicle deer whistles have a dual construction and a single mounting seat for better deer repelling. No electricity required. It's powered by wind. The deer alarm automatically emits ultrasonic waves at speeds of more than 35 miles per hour during the day or night and alerts from a quarter mile away.

【Size Information】: Each deer alarm device is 2×1.6×0.87 inches in size and comes with 2 or 4 whistles per pack, and they can be easily affixed to various types of bumpers or grilles. These discreetly designed devices blend seamlessly with your vehicle's aesthetics while remaining inconspicuous.

【Universal Fit】: These deer whistles are universally designed to be compatible with cars, SUVs, trucks, motorcycles, ATVs, and more. Simply remove the adhesive backing and apply the whistle to the grille. Ensure that two holes forward and the deer whistle is level with the horizon.
